Welcome to the blog app.

Introduction to the app
This blog app shows a collection of articles which can be selected based on topics or can be sorted based on date, votes, comment count 
in ascending or descending order. You can choose a single article to read, add comments and votes to the article. 
If an incorrect path is choosen, or a non-existent topic is requested, error handling is in place to inform the user of the error.


Links 
Here is the link to the frontend repository - 
Here is the link to the backend repository - https://nc-news-bp.onrender.com


Instructions to run this project locally
1. Node version of atleast v18.16.0 is required. 
2. Clone the repository by git clone <repo-url>
3. install npm and start the app using npm run dev


